      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**Question 4b.** Go back up to Module 3 to find this exact sum. What can we conclude about the probability of relative primeness? This is <span style="color:red;">**Module 3 in action**!</span> 🚀"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "zgoZnW1VTKpV"
