      "id": "GkRj_gJWHIS-",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "GkRj_gJWHIS-"
      },
      "source": [
        "Let's explore this a little further through understanding *error*. Note that we have:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$f(\\theta) = \\pi-\\theta \\approx 2 \\sum_{n=1}^N \\frac{\\sin (n\\theta)}{n}$$\n",
        "\n",
        "Let's estimate the **error** in this approximation using the function $g_N(\\theta)$:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$g_N(\\theta) = 2\\sum_{n=1}^N \\frac{\\sin (n\\theta)}{n} - (\\pi-\\theta) $$\n",
        "\n",
        "Again, let's plot this by running the code below."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "def g_N(N_terms, M=2000):\n",
        "    # Calculate S_N(x) and f(x) over the plotting range\n",
        "    x_plot = np.linspace(-2 * np.pi, 4 * np.pi, M)\n",
        "    x_for_f = np.mod(x_plot, 2 * np.pi)\n",
        "    fx_actual = f_sawtooth(x_for_f)\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Use the partial_sum function to get S_N(x)\n",
        "    _, _, S = partial_sum(f_sawtooth, N_terms=N_terms, M=M)\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Calculate the error g_N(theta)\n",
        "    error_gn = S - fx_actual\n",
        "    return x_plot, error_gn\n",
        "\n",
        "# ---------- Interactive UI for g_N(theta) ----------\n",
        "N_error_widget = widgets.IntSlider(\n",
        "    value=1, min=1, max=100, step=1,\n",
        "    description=\"N terms (error plot):\",\n",
        "    continuous_update=False,\n",
        "    style={\"description_width\": \"initial\"},\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "error_out = widgets.Output()\n",
        "\n",
        "def render_error(_=None):\n",
        "    with error_out:\n",
        "        error_out.clear_output(wait=True)\n",
        "\n",
        "        N = N_error_widget.value\n",
        "        M_grid = 2000 # Fixed grid for plotting\n",
        "\n",
        "        x_plot, error_values = g_N(N, M=M_grid)\n",
        "\n",
        "        plt.figure()\n",
        "        plt.plot(x_plot, error_values, label=f\"g_N(theta), N={N}\", color='red')\n",
        "        plt.grid(True)\n",
        "        plt.legend()\n",
        "        plt.title(f\"Error Function g_N(theta) for f(theta)=pi-theta (N={N})\")\n",
        "        plt.xlabel(\"theta\")\n",
        "        plt.ylabel(\"g_N(theta)\")\n",
        "        plt.xlim(-2 * np.pi, 4 * np.pi) # Consistent x-limits\n",
        "        plt.axhline(0, color='black', linewidth=0.5)\n",
        "        plt.show()\n",
        "\n",
        "N_error_widget.observe(render_error, names=\"value\")\n",
        "\n",
        "error_controls = widgets.VBox([\n",
        "    N_error_widget,\n",
        "])\n",
        "\n",
        "display(error_controls, error_out)\n",
        "render_error()\n"
      ],
